يبًۭا ۖ","translation":"কিছুকাল","audioUrl":"wbw/059_015_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17372,"position":6,"arabic":"ذَاقُوا۟","translation":"তারা স্বাদ নিয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/059_015_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17373,"position":7,"arabic":"وَبَالَ","translation":"কুফলের","audioUrl":"wbw/059_015_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17374,"position":8,"arabic":"أَمْرِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের কাজের","audioUrl":"wbw/059_015_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17375,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَهُمْ","translation":"ও তাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/059_015_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17376,"position":10,"arabic":"عَذَابٌ","translation":"আজাব","audioUrl":"wbw/059_015_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17377,"position":11,"arabic":"أَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"কষ্টদায়ক","audioUrl":"wbw/059_015_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17378,"position":12,"arabic":"١٥","translation":"(১৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":16,"arabic":"كَمَثَلِ ٱلشَّيْطَٰنِ إِذْ قَالَ لِلْإِنسَٰنِ ٱكْفُرْ فَلَمَّا كَفَرَ قَالَ إِنِّى بَرِىٓءٌۭ مِّنكَ إِنِّىٓ أَخَافُ ٱللَّهَ رَبَّ ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"the like of [what happens] when Satan says unto man, “Deny the truth!” - but as soon as [man] has denied the truth, [Satan] says, “Behold, I am not responsible for thee: behold, I fear God, the Sustainer of all the worlds!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5142.mp3","surahId":59,"words":[{"id":18431,"position":1,"arabic":"كَمَثَلِ","translation":"দৃষ্ঠান্ত যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/059_016_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":18432,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنِ","translation":"শয়তানের","audioUrl":"wbw/059_016_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":18433,"position":3,"arabic":"إِذْ","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/059_016_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":18434,"position":4,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/059_016_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":18435,"position":5,"arabi